      "para_id": "Q004980.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Ur-Enlil , child of Šarrum-bani , the general , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
